{"tid":764188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲反移民情緒高漲    黑人鐵餅女將遭打傷眼","createTime":"2018-08-01T17:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T00:13:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b31dd151bfbf24c466c4a26f113bb696dced704","tid":764188,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T17:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180801/large/1533128507_a2b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180801%2Flarge%2F1533128507_a2b6.jpg&h=963e6a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐洲部份地區反移民情緒高漲，就連非洲裔運動員亦深受其害。最新一宗是擁有意大利國籍的尼日利亞裔鐵餅運動員奧薩琪，周一在都靈遭到不明人士擲蛋攻擊，使她的眼部受傷，很可能影響她出戰下周在德國柏林舉行的歐洲田徑錦標賽。目前當地政府已介入調查事件，不排除與種族歧視有關。"},{"pid":"0313f1e9114035ba8ae8c96093d407ff66c6c3ac","tid":764188,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:13:22.000Z","msg":"極左》極右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}